item.title: CVE-2022-1627|2024-08-03T00:10:03.670Z -- unknown -- my%20private%20site
item.description: The My Private Site WordPress plugin before 3.0.8 does not have CSRF check in place when updating its settings, which could allow attackers to make a logged in admin change them via a CSRF attack
